ebol.org/view-script.r?script=3kbnewsreader.r">3kbnewsreader.r</a></td><td style="text-align: right;font-size: 85%" class="lsdata1">v:0.1.1<br>4.3&nbsp;KB<br>13&nbsp;Mar&nbsp;2003</td><td class="lsdata1 code" style="padding:1em;">Simple CLI news reader.<br><span style="font-weight:bold">author: Ryan C. Christiansen</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan="3" style="border-bottom: thin blue solid !important; padding-top: 1em" class="lsdata2">A Reb-Site</td></tr><tr><td class="lsdata2"><a href="http://www.rebol.org/view-script.r?script=a-reb-site.r">a-reb-site.r</a></td><td style="text-align: right;font-size: 85%" class="lsdata2">v:0.1.1<br>70.8&nbsp;KB<br>23&nbsp;Mar&nbsp;2008</td><td class="lsdata2 code" style="padding:1em;">a-reb-site.r was written to:
               -  compare form and function of a reb-site with that of a conventional web-site.
                  (...an obliging web-site - www.rebol.com perhaps&#033;) &amp; 
